Cipher & Row - Freight Verification MCP
=======================================

What is open (this repository, MIT licensed)
--------------------------------------------
- The tool JSON Schemas in `schemas/`.
- The client configuration files in `mcp-config/`.
- The documentation and examples in `docs/` and `examples/`.

These describe the public interface of the Cipher & Row MCP server so that
developers and AI agents can integrate against a stable, documented contract.
The live server at https://mcp.cipherandrow.com/mcp is the authoritative source
of truth; this repository is kept in sync with it.

